CiBemaFD1tXvosQCsey92cf4/-sGEb74BcpJNgrxpC6QPdjDNVUTqns-Y/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="联合国警告称，对伊朗基础设施的袭击有违反法律的风险"&gt;战争罪，&lt;/a&gt;因为他承诺摧毁伊朗的民用基础设施，这可能违反了国际法。周二，特朗普更进一步，承诺“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/9Yxl_nEulVmuC1nIVm4wEwiKD5_lQgb94kC7z035KxThl9wb8eS7OUO79GvESihzT943DSX_gTatlIf8uUjO06O5MGDszWkKiBhHN1TLy_ZlhNpigJFEQGET_vTDKa8Dy-Sjp2HCfqtCgLnSRT8wPeOfXBtX1hcTIPh4VJy0G_gsCjTd4xLrtswMPzxbooRqMh2-2p9CQ8GFkTQTEke5TBA5hAFJA6iStRynzOejSsr9CdyEtbkBqAmd2yJjDe9_Q0qZ_Ki85NuLNyOFW4qIDGdBgDO9_CniTLWJU21oR4mA_vw5tBnezx5yZqRgYkVImE7xXwM7SwIJtUDPzWHX4FvMGoG9elCraaoZuJS2Iaxiv2dJWtShayNSGMBk3BMVtSXFZYr5_mFSi5VC9Az0DXosLESLJceUrvL69OouGokI9lfBtMmqOG5TJQy6PfAo45osAHtihNxmm3Ej8sz_7ZxiXw2bHyRDdYYVZdC3D6cneBJgRDQffKgEubpvgEz8Z9F21w/BoZhr8tDC7b0hD4gOluWStP40P85xrDk/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着最后期限临近，特朗普重申摧毁伊朗的威胁"&gt;整个文明今晚将消亡&lt;/a&gt;”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;尽管特朗普一再未能落实他在深夜社交媒体上发布的许多帖子，但今天的世界末日警告却引发了一些人对核武器的担忧（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Yx6FNF99O--BFBxpZtgEeeli4iChBvIcC8nlYyjp4JOCf4RdDpA1eDiBNnUm6xKHy1QFWfQzDqpgkN9Hhv4CrqlFqN_Z1bVRzSaGVCdPqPxhX-1gUl3TOy8HeC_6ihAKcDudp4EIV_XnfUxQ6BQNKwVUTtQae3q7SgSD4JMKEnGu31JN2SB60vdrlwLMOQZxrzdfEHu_f1PCsdQp72bphEEzA4bI6M7bxPEnmclkMorbGH1ns8RjZgqIifiuQ_Z9GMhUr0c-FyszKzjAtddb-GoYMO2optuNQfrm2OkMbGioj0Qurf6yhui8rOx5Ze-aJ9rJd2NRl4l0rLjNN4_epL3UH9jbvs1kYe4NyV_H-FEAGHUS/rCMSd7fqK_v8W42ak_w3wfw3sRiN4slb/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="白宫猛烈抨击特朗普在伊朗使用核武器的说法"&gt;据报道白宫对此予以否认&lt;/a&gt;）。当这一切在有线电视新闻频道上播出时，美国和以色列继续轰炸伊朗，袭击其&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Q1sYCJXYFJbg-XTOlf4t0QSvBFOloxn5pZAcp7dSZvcw1H56ReIh414becd3Wpurk8h5xv6e1_ArS2NS3TKZXfKIlJHffM-lWWe62HIa_0ftsS1_uQMaMjYNJUMc2qrLdvl4h-3I50H4sOflTPpKrvAjBvcViGgEDHtxAW8QZ-bSUBQuD8TC6KurIUCnAiukA2yb9-8n4YrciuzFneD0aeifD