&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在特朗普的伊朗最后期限临近之际，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;由于油价上涨，美国国债下跌&lt;/strong&gt;。此次下跌使收益率上升了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/teU20Kh5ia1BosTm_bBrhFJ_0cj7jnWHlyrOuNrIVmNkVEYsUwqA-NIZt6SjrqCRaIHd2UXyb9vtXc9TFC7QLKOR4cwDoDbftTW5d15-frpVJPTGmJQiXjFQx7dow9UoIkfKhuXS9bWe3esS0ul8APXmPmd5uAcay95mH7FqozcGKQmBGDHmduntQwK4GZ1jk-22ICgeFSiDYjvspQbAVSe8hzW5EodV6NsXk7oheoZGSHDdxa_jRIRrVU4Vz1ulXehRKT1-BAMUkXZTHdBfPv3XSPb8mmkQv9FpwJIRGKJ8ima0BFqUF-lFcx0qg4nHCsjFnMTjw00PZ-WJXkf1zSw0gRaMy7P2r4JVPVSx14WCJ7mPecgQI3_ZutLnQwiJXQWqNx07wUI6zmJlnSKjpCVr4AvQgWDANEZV7p4FRfNWaoQlC7AsLdIeMQ_NbazdIF5Cg35ket_QbK2z-LoRFaWEVW2VNwJ6akZpxQSY3t2BDBU-oR55sOrtXAyOzQGVJ2vS/dnhbrgf9HHJYbu1wbTztPspOvwhOpTcx/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争推动石油上涨、风险降低，国债下跌"&gt;多达五个基点&lt;/a&gt;，其中长期期限的涨幅最大。围绕特朗普大规模杀伤性威胁是否可能实现的一系列相互矛盾的信号，十年期和三十年期国债收益率创下盘中高点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/8zTCXaUbxEtCPBcKd91SMJa6nA90e7aDodZmbljLH_3uBh5PdN91lduSQxD5szzGxrzOoeIyP9epvhGKcbLi98EHHtUh6hduR6VbYyO228DoUa1dWu3vNyHwJ8i5mI7751QCK1egpOVhxsgbnXiaLmfSIYG5tWVFIJUbHpdKSpg-jaNMVKnqP-pNSNZdrDHxl3Ke76uBt7K0sy_Zzp2Ay-iGN8Ao99c5GhtbRPFLroZR1vln_WLSl01fL71KexiFdzcXXvW6YXBVw_8MXLu74feX4qNOd_FnFnwZbKjPg4hFpn4VM-CU1nX0eNiLMg5STqO27arxzQdQvyDiiZ6Frg8o7f6fvYp_mAdV59pk4vOlYh9eZA65LVwTogOtRSFx9ouRterEr_0YWIw8gA/BxwFYef-NKYobOW15VHAATkZjXK1o0KK/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTL5JpOF.xJY/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTL5JpOF.xJY/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-